      "topic": "Matching Definitions",
      "question": "Read each definition and all four choices carefully, and find the answer that provides the best example of the given definition.\nApplying for Seasonal Employment occurs when a person requests to be considered for a job that is dependent on a particular season or time of year. Which situation below is the best example of Applying for Seasonal Employment?",
      "options": [
