      "question": "Each problem consists of three statements. Based on the first two statements, the third statement may be true, false, or uncertain.\nAll the tulips in Zoe's garden are white. All the pansies in Zoe's garden are yellow. All the flowers in Zoe's garden are either white or yellow If the first two statements are true, the third statement is",
      "options": [
        "true",
        "false",
        "uncertain"
      ],
      "correct": "uncertain",
      "section": "logical"
    },
