      "id": "logical-0134",
      "topic": "Logical Problems",
      "question": "Each problem consists of three statements. Based on the first two statements, the third statement may be true, false, or uncertain.\nDuring the past year, Josh saw more movies than Stephen. Stephen saw fewer movies than Darren. Darren saw more movies than Josh. If the first two statements are true, the third statement is",
