      "question": "In each question below is given a statement followed by two assumptions numbered I and II. You have to consider the statement and the following assumptions and decide which of the assumptions is implicit in the statement. \nStatement: It is desirable to put the child in school at the age of 5 or so. Assumptions: 1. At that age the child reaches appropriate level of development and is ready to learn. 2. The schools do not admit children after six years of age.",
