      "question": "Each of the following questions contains a small paragraph followed by a question on it. Read each paragraph carefully and answer the question given below it.\nThe attainment of individual and organisational goals is mutually interdependent and linked by a common denominator - employee work motivation. Organisational members are motivated to satisfy their personal goals, and they contribute their efforts to the attainment of organisational objectives as means of achieving these personal goals. The passage best supports the statement that motivation -",
